channel.title: The best 317 base which looks like a 420# is here! 5000+ downloads!
channel.description:
.•*´¨) `¸.•´¸.•*´¨)¸.•*¨) (¸.•´ (¸.• Unholy Blitz is a RS2 server that I began coding like 2 weeks ago but I got pretty damn tired of it, which made me release it.
If you want a stable PK server this is what you've been looking for :)
TO ALL YOU NERDS CALLING ME LEACHER: GTFO, I ADDED ABOUT 10 NEW FEATURES! DOWNLOAD AND SEE IF YOU THINK I LIE!
-------------
Features:
- The best PvP combat you ever will see! :cool:
- All weapon specials 100% ( look yourself if you don't believe) :eek:
- over 2000 npc's added! Doesn't even lagg a shit! :P (if you're lucky bcuz some people have complained bout lagg)
- All Combat skills :|
- Ranging projectiles, good ranging, stable :cool:
- Prayer 100% :eek:
- Mining :eek: :P
- Agility :eek:
- Herblore :eek:
- Brimhaven Dungeon :D
- Stable base ;)
- Void armour, Bandos armour, Armadyl Armour and more. Forgot to add Rune c'bow :confused:
- No customs like godswords, statius, dragon platebody. :rolleyes:
- Good starting armour :)
- Alching+100% spellbook :eek: (working teleblock) awesomeness? ;D
!!---------------!!
Client Features:
- New Attack interface
- New Emote interface
- New Magic interface
- New Prayer interface
- Equipment screen interface
- Dragon 2h Stance
